      <direction placement="above">
        <direction-type>
          <words default-y="31.73" relative-y="10.00">And if there was a good way to make it sound &quot;strummier&quot; short of adding invisible arpeggios to every note,
</words>
          <words>that would be great. MuseScore isn't designed for this style of music.</words>
          </direction-type>
        </direction>
